name: I Wanna Go Home! (A-Jar-Of-Peanuts)
description:
Uh oh, You get isekai'd into a fantasy world after getting hit by a truck! You are told that in order to return home, you need to defeat the three Demon Lords that terrorize this alternate universe. But maybe there's a better more peaceful solution to this predicament?
